---
title: Double Miso-Ginger Chicken & Peanut Salad with Sesame Fries
description: Amp up the flavour to ten by glazing tender chicken in a miso and ginger sauce. Push the crunch factor to the top with a peanut
cucumber salad and sesame seeds on the oven-baked fries. This dish has successfully maxed out its flavour!
